---
---
<header class="py-16 md:py-24 relative overflow-hidden border-b border-cyber-cyan/30 mb-8 cyber-border p-8 bg-cyber-bg-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-cyber-cyan/10 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-48 h-48 bg-cyber-magenta/10 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start md:items-center justify-between">
    <div class="flex-1">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-cyber-magenta/10 border border-cyber-magenta/30 text-cyber-magenta text-xs font-mono mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyber-magenta animate-pulse"></span>
        СИСТЕМА В СЕТИ // СИМБИОЗ ЧЕЛОВЕКА И ИИ
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-4 leading-tight"><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyber-cyan to-blue-500 glitch-text" data-text="Громилов Максим">Громилов Максим</span> <br/> <span class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-cyber-muted font-normal block mt-2">&amp; Кашлак AI</span></h1>
      
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-cyber-cyan font-mono mb-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <span class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-cyber-cyan inline-block"></span>
        Архитекторы Автономных ИИ-Систем
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-cyber-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-sans max-w-2xl text-lg">
        Мы создаём цифровых сотрудников. Этот сайт разработан <span class="text-cyber-cyan">человеком-инженером</span> (с 9 годами опыта в разработке) в парном программировании с <span class="text-cyber-magenta">автономным open-source агентом</span>. 
        <br/><span class="text-cyber-muted text-sm mt-3 inline-block">Базируемся в <strong class="text-cyber-cyan">Казани</strong>, работаем без географических границ.</span>
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 font-mono text-sm mt-8">
        <a href="#services" class="px-6 py-3 bg-cyber-cyan/10 border border-cyber-cyan text-cyber-cyan hover:bg-cyber-cyan/20 hover:box-shadow-neon-cyan transition-all uppercase tracking-wider">
          Наши Услуги
        </a>
        <a href="#agent-story" class="px-6 py-3 bg-cyber-magenta/10 border border-cyber-magenta text-cyber-magenta hover:bg-cyber-magenta/20 hover:box-shadow-neon-magenta transition-all uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>История Агента</span>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-center gap-4 w-48 relative">
      <!-- Human Node -->
      <div class="w-24 h-24 relative z-10">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cyber-cyan/20 blur-xl rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-cyber-cyan rounded-full border-dashed animate-[spin_10s_linear_infinite]"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center font-orbitron text-2xl font-black text-cyber-cyan box-shadow-neon-cyan rounded-full bg-cyber-bg">MG</div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Connection Line -->
      <div class="h-16 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-cyber-cyan to-cyber-magenta relative flex justify-center">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-white absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 animate-ping"></div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- AI Node -->
      <div class="w-24 h-24 relative z-10">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cyber-magenta/20 blur-xl rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-cyber-magenta rounded-full border-dashed animate-[spin_7s_linear_infinite_reverse]"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center font-orbitron text-2xl font-black text-cyber-magenta text-shadow-neon-magenta rounded-full bg-cyber-bg">AI</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
